cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper proposes a novel exploration method for deep reinforcement learning, specifically in the context of distributional RL. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which encompasses topics related to deep learning and RL. Additionally, the paper uses Atari 2600 games and a 3D driving simulator as experimental environments, which suggests that it may also fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also mentions using image-based inputs, which could place it under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper discusses safety rewards, which could indicate a connection to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
